{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"## WS8 LIVE CUTOVER COMPLETE + VERIFIED (2026-07-01)\n\nExecuted on the production Gerrit box (i-00880b2c7f13527c5) via AWS SSM after PR #112 merged.\n\n### What was done\n1. **Bot HTTP password** — already provisioned in S4a (SSM /rebar/prod/gerrit-bot-token);\n   verified working PRE-flip (HTTP 200). No action needed — DB-only service user survives OAUTH.\n2. **Durable admin lever** — registered a session admin SSH key on account 1000000 (Administrators)\n   via the tested bootstrap-gerrit-admin.sh (NoteDb, auth-mode-independent). Key at\n   /root/.ssh/gerrit_admin on the box (root-only) — a break-glass admin path that survives OAUTH.\n3. **Synced merged-main files** to the box's stale /opt/rebar (gerrit.config, compose-up.sh,\n   fetch-secrets.sh, install-plugins.sh) so a later compose-up cannot revert the flip.\n4. **Installed oauth.jar** via install-plugins.sh — sha256 VERIFIED on disk\n   (2bcf58a652fe5e513d7a4c73362dfc5d9a3dc697f699a5280416ae6f86d0242f), 4,077,624 bytes.\n5. **Flipped** via compose-up.sh: materialized client-id into gerrit.config + merged client-secret\n   into secure.config (Gerrit's own registerEmailPrivateKey PRESERVED — the merge, not clobber),\n   restarted gerrit. Backup at /var/gerrit/site/etc/gerrit.config.pre-ws8.bak for rollback.\n\n### Verification (Step 6) — 3/4 mechanical checks PASS\n- auth_type == OAUTH (public via nginx AND internal). ✅\n- gerrit-oauth-provider plugin ENABLED (clean load in error_log). ✅\n- Anonymous /a/ -> 401; /login/ -> 302 to github.com/login/oauth/authorize with the correct\n  client_id (0v23liqRBRUUf7wZQqPr) + redirect_uri (…/oauth). DEVELOPMENT_BECOME_ANY_ACCOUNT GONE. ✅\n- rebar-review-bot HTTP auth still works POST-flip (HTTP 200, acct 1000002). ✅\n- All plugins ENABLED; both containers Up; review-bot restarted clean (health 200, no degraded). ✅\n\n### Remaining (needs a human)\n- **\"Human logs in via GitHub\"** — requires interactive GitHub OAuth consent in a browser\n  (can't be done headlessly). Once a human logs in, their new Gerrit account can be added to\n  Administrators via admin SSH (I hold the lever). This is the last Step-6 item before closing WS8."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782933965397165001,"uuid":"fb37e8cf-1507-4ee1-ad7f-750102a07a00"}